  "detailed_description": "<h1>ATTENTION!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989860/extras/d9563d77023f1c0dde521e0691615241.avif?t=1772923976\" width=780 height=154 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Imagine waking up in a chicken coop, shackled. In front of you there is a game machine with a chicken egg and a counter. To get free from this strange place you need to show attention and wit!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989860/extras/2dad5c45c5fe286b479bf7e83f4f630a.poster.avif?t=1772923976\" width=780 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989860/extras/2dad5c45c5fe286b479bf7e83f4f630a.webm?t=1772923976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989860/extras/2dad5c45c5fe286b479bf7e83f4f630a.mp4?t=1772923976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A survival horror clicker! Why not?<br></li><li> Chickens. Lots of chickens.<br></li><li> Elements of a puzzle. You'll have to use your head to save yourself and the chicken egg.<br></li><li> Separate controls for each of the arms.<br></li><li> Retro-styled graphics.</li></ul><br><i>If you need a little hint, check out the news about the game's release.</i>",
